                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/9631" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">HRM-0620</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1346 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">善作善成，革故鼎新:新联谊事务所助力泰山索道薪酬体系改革</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Generate Outstanding Work and Revolutionize Conventional Approaches:XINLIANYI Certified Public Accountants LLP Supports the Reform of Salary System in Taishan Cableway</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">徐英杰，陈一帆，周敬毅</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">济南大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">新联谊会计师事务所（特殊普通合伙）</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">科研、咨询业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">人力资源部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">16 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">薪酬体系；岗位绩效考核；薪酬激励</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Salary system; Post performance appraisal; Salary incentive</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本案例描述了新联谊事务所助力泰山索道进行薪酬体系改革的工作思路与主要内容，系统总结了国有企业薪酬体系改革的设计框架、主要过程和关键内容。案例分析了“激励有效、公平均衡、重点突出、价值贡献、按劳分配”的薪酬体系设计原则，总结岗位重构、价值评估、薪级划分、序列并行、任务分解与考核反馈等环节的主要工作内容，为国有企业结合产业布局和运营模式设计灵活的薪酬体系和多元化的激励措施提供了经验证据，并结合职业发展双通道理论，进一步剖析新联谊事务所协助泰山索道设计序列并行的原因及作用。本案例通过将薪酬设计与岗位绩效考核的核心知识点应用于实际情境中，培养学生解决问题的能力，促进理论与实践的深度融合。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">This case describes the working ideas and main contents of XINLIANYI Certified Public Accountants LLP to help Taishan Cableway carry out salary system reform, and systematically summarizes the design framework, main process and key contents of the salary system reform of state-owned enterprises. The design principles of salary  system with &quot;effective incentives, fair and balanced, focused, value contribution and distribution according to work&quot; are analyzed, and the main work contents of post reconstruction, value evaluation, salary scale division, sequence parallelism, task decomposition and assessment feedback are summarized, which provides empirical evidence for state-owned enterprises to design flexible salary system and diversified incentive measures in combination with industrial layout and operation mode. Combined with the dual-channel theory of career development, the reasons and functions of XINLIANYI Certified Public Accountants LLP in assisting Taishan Cableway design sequence parallelism are further analyzed. In this case, the core knowledge points of salary design and post performance appraisal are applied to the actual situation to cultivate students&#39; problem-solving ability and promote the deep integration of theory and practice.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《人力资源管理》、《薪酬管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">薪酬体系类型选择；国有企业薪酬体系设计的目标；薪酬结构原理；薪酬设计与绩效激励；职能部门分类管理；绩效指标设计与作用；关键绩效指标考核法；薪酬等级划分；薪酬带宽设定</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-05</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
